---
// B2B Hero — sterk acquisitie-gericht, geen werkzoekenden-kanaal
---

<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-proman-navy via-proman-navy to-proman-navy-dark text-white overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04] pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, white 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 24px 24px;" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute -top-32 -right-32 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-proman-orange/15 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-proman-orange/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container-app relative pt-12 pb-16 md:pt-20 md:pb-24 lg:pt-28 lg:pb-32">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-proman-orange rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
          50.000+ werkgevers vertrouwen op PROMAN
        </div>

        <h1 class="heading-xl mb-6 text-balance">
          De HR-partner die <span class="text-proman-orange-light">levert</span> wanneer jouw groei het vraagt.
        </h1>

        <p class="lead text-white/85 mb-8 max-w-2xl text-balance">
          Productiepieken, sleutelvacatures, payroll-complexiteit, executive opvolging — zes gespecialiseerde merken onder één dak. Antwoord binnen 24 uur, kandidaat binnen 48.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 mb-10">
          <a href="/offerte/" class="btn-primary btn-large">
            Vraag een offerte
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/diensten/" class="border-2 border-white/30 hover:border-white text-white font-semibold px-6 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors text-center">
            Verken onze diensten
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-8 max-w-xl pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
          <div>
            <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-proman-orange-light">48u</div>
            <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/70 mt-1">Gemiddelde invultijd</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-proman-orange-light">170+</div>
            <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/70 mt-1">Lokale kantoren</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-proman-orange-light">92%</div>
            <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/70 mt-1">Klant-retentie / 1jr</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Quick contact form -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="bg-white text-proman-navy rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-2xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-proman-orange">Snel antwoord</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-proman-mint text-green-800 font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full flex items-center gap-1">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-600 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span> Reactie binnen 1 werkdag
            </span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="heading-sm mb-2">Vertel kort wat je nodig hebt</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-proman-navy/70 mb-5">Een lokale consulent met sectorkennis belt je terug. Geen verkoopgesprek, wel een concreet voorstel.</p>
          <form class="space-y-3" data-quick-form>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <input type="text" placeholder="Voornaam" required class="border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-proman-orange focus:border-proman-orange outline-none" />
              <input type="text" placeholder="Bedrijf" required class="border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-proman-orange focus:border-proman-orange outline-none" />
            </div>
            <input type="email" placeholder="E-mail" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-proman-orange outline-none" />
            <input type="tel" placeholder="Telefoon" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-proman-orange outline-none" />
            <select class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-proman-orange outline-none">
              <option>Wat heb je nodig?</option>
              <option>Tijdelijk personeel (uitzend)</option>
              <option>Vaste werving</option>
              <option>Payroll-uitbesteding</option>
              <option>Executive search</option>
              <option>Outplacement</option>
              <option>Talent assessment</option>
              <option>Iets anders / advies</option>
            </select>
            <button type="submit" class="w-full btn-primary py-3.5">
              Stuur aanvraag →
            </button>
            <p class="text-xs text-proman-navy/50 text-center">Door te versturen ga je akkoord met onze <a href="#" class="underline">privacy-voorwaarden</a>.</p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelector('form[data-quick-form]')?.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    alert('Demo: aanvraag verstuurd. In productie: connect met CRM/email-API.');
  });
</script>
